      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks.. i was kinda worried it was something more serious like a stroke or something but honestly i get these really bad ones sometimes. you think it's just a migraine then? what should i take for it? i have some extra strength ibuprofen and some naproxen in my cabinet, can i just take a bunch of both to make it stop faster?",
